latestPosts.caption:
This hair secret went viral for a reason, and even a year later, I’m still obsessed with the @lorealparis Glycolic Gloss range ✨🎀

#paidpartnership #glycolicgloss #glasshair #shinyhair #lorealparis #hairtok

Here’s why: Caffeine stimulates your follicles and may help fight the effects of DHT (aka the hair loss hormone) ☕️✨ if you’re dealing with hair thinning or shedding this ingredient might just change your routine 👀 

#hairgrowth #hairtips #beautyhacks

You might have seen me using a lot a lot of @theouai products lately and that’s because I’m obsessed ✨ 

• The scalp serum is sooo nice, I apply it most nights before bed.

• St Barts Leave In Conditioner smells incredible and leaves my hair soooo soft.

• Melrose Place body moisturiser is just 10/10. 

• The wide tooth comb is so good for brushing out curls, and I carry it everywhere in my handbag with me.

#haircare #hairroutine #theouai #showerroutine
